result.title: Congrats My Ex!
result.author: Benetone Films
result.description: Risa, who runs a wedding planning company, along with her close-knit circle of friends including Jan and Aoffy. They find themselves tasked with orchestrating a grand wedding for Arun and Monica, an Indian newlywed couple who have brought along a substantial entourage of relatives to conduct their ceremony in Thailand. With Tim serving as the event's photographer, this Indian wedding extravaganza is poised to be filled with turmoil as former lovers reunite.
